---
source: crates/carta/tests/golden_e2e.rs
expression: output
---
\begin{description}
\item[\texttt{-a}]
Output all.
\item[\texttt{-b,\ -\/-brief}]
Be brief about it.
\item[\texttt{-\/-verbose}]
Talk a great deal.
\item[\texttt{-f\ FILE}]
Read input from FILE.
\end{description}

The description may also start on the next line:

\begin{description}
\item[\texttt{-\/-output=FILE}]
Write output to FILE instead of standard output.
\end{description}
